<plot>Hershel has a thing for Emily. She's half his age, though, and would never even consider going on a date with him. Instead, she sets Hershel up with Penny, her older sister. When he decides to bail on their date, Penny dies of a broken heart. Though guilt ridden at first, Hershel quickly realizes this could actually be the perfect opportunity to win Emily over.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237446</url></doc>
